Job Descriptions:
 Carrying out maintenance, repairing and servicing tasks
 To carry out preventive / breakdown and corrective maintenance of M&amp;E
 Attend to defects and complains promptly
 Perform any other ad hoc duties assigned

Job Requirements:
 Minimum 2 years and above in Facilities Management environment
 Possess at least ITE / NTC certification in Mechanical / Air-Con / Electrical / Facility Management
 Honest, committed and hardworking individual
 Able to commit within a short notice